Sentencas: Agglomeration behavior of nickel particles on yttria stabilized zirconia (YSZ).
Titulo: Agglomeration behavior of nickel particles on YSZ electrolyte

Sentencas: NiO doped YSZ and TiO2 doped YSZ substrates was examined by scanning electron microscopy (SEM) as two dimensional (2D) analysis and scanning probe microscopy (SPM) as three-dimensional (3D) analysis.
Titulo: Agglomeration behavior of nickel particles on YSZ electrolyte

Sentencas: For 2D analysis, binarized SEM image was analyzed to examine the agglomeration factor.
Titulo: Agglomeration behavior of nickel particles on YSZ electrolyte

Sentencas: In 3D analysis, wettability analyzing method was adopted for solid particle on solid substrate, and apparent contact angle was evaluated by the following equation; theta = 2 tan(-1) (2 h/d) where d and h are the observed particle diameter and the observed particle height of each agglomerated particle obtained by SPM analysis.
Titulo: Agglomeration behavior of nickel particles on YSZ electrolyte

Sentencas: Results from both analysis techniques revealed that NiO doped YSZ tend to enhance the nickel agglomeration, whereas TiO2 doped YSZ shows better wettability especially for larger nickel particles.
Titulo: Agglomeration behavior of nickel particles on YSZ electrolyte
